Attribution:
------------

These templates are based on Common Paper standards, originally created by
a committee of over 40 attorneys representing technology vendors,
procurement teams, boutique firms, and Big Law. Source repositories:

  * Mutual Non-Disclosure Agreement — https://github.com/CommonPaper/Mutual-NDA
  * Cloud Service Agreement       — https://github.com/CommonPaper/CSA
  * Design Partner Agreement      — https://github.com/CommonPaper/Design-Partner-Agreement
  * Service Level Agreement       — https://github.com/CommonPaper/SLA
  * Professional Services Agreement — https://github.com/CommonPaper/PSA
  * Data Processing Agreement     — https://github.com/CommonPaper/DPA
  * Software License Agreement    — https://github.com/CommonPaper/Software-License-Agreement
  * Partnership Agreement         — https://github.com/CommonPaper/Partnership-Agreement
  * Pilot Agreement               — https://github.com/CommonPaper/Pilot-Agreement
  * Business Associate Agreement  — https://github.com/CommonPaper/BAA
  * AI Addendum                   — https://github.com/CommonPaper/AI-Addendum

Catalog:
  * catalog.json — name, description, and filename for each template in this
    directory.

No warranty:
------------

These templates are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. They are
not a substitute for legal advice. Consult a qualified attorney before
executing any agreement based on these templates.